questionAnswerPair.question: Who are you?
questionAnswerPair.answer: I am Rover, loyal companion and longtime resident of this computer!

questionAnswerPair.question: Where am I?
questionAnswerPair.answer: You're in a computer, of course.

questionAnswerPair.question: How do I get out of here?
questionAnswerPair.answer: Hmm...the last person to get stuck here mailed themselves out...

questionAnswerPair.question: Help?
questionAnswerPair.answer: Have you checked out the folders on this computer? My user spends a lot of time in music and photos.

questionAnswerPair.question: Help?
questionAnswerPair.answer: Have you checked out the folders on this computer? My user plays some game in the games folder all the time...I forget the name...Why don't you check it out?

questionAnswerPair.question: Help?
questionAnswerPair.answer: If you've checked out all the files on this computer, why don't you give email a look?

questionAnswerPair.question: How do I reach the files?
questionAnswerPair.answer: Well, I jump, but I'm a dog. Maybe you could get some practice playing the games on this computer.

questionAnswerPair.question: Why is the music folder important?
questionAnswerPair.answer: There's this one artist my user's been listening to a lot lately...I can't remember their name...

questionAnswerPair.question: Why is the pictures folder important?
questionAnswerPair.answer: If only my user loved me as much as my user loves their real dog...

questionAnswerPair.question: Why is the writings folder important?
questionAnswerPair.answer: My user's been spending a lot of time trying to solve puzzles lately. Spotted lanternfly? Ant? Ladybug? Oh, woof it! I can't remember the name. There's some number at the end too...

questionAnswerPair.question: Why am I locked out of email?
questionAnswerPair.answer: Have you been guessing random passwords?! I'll give you a hint: it's not abc123. Why don't you spend time collecting information about my user?
